revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}

An inline formatting template primarily meant to handle the linewrapping of groupnames in {{tl|Navbox}}es or relatively long entries in infoboxes and sidebars. It reduces the padding between the text and the edge of the cell, minimizing the height of the <code>group</code> parameter.

== Parameters ==
* {{para|1}} - The item, i.e. the text to display
* {{para|style}} - Additional [[CSS]] code for styling

== Tracking categories ==
* {{Category link with count|Pages using Template:Longitem with unnamed style parameter}}

== See also ==
* {{tl|longlink}}

<includeonly>{{Sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line, please: -->
[[Category:Inline templates]]
[[Category:Text-specific formatting and function templates]]
}}</includeonly>

